{
  "id": "RAW_8c9270",
  "title": "免费功能卷翻付费版 ChatGPT，欧洲 AI 新贵叫板 OpenAI",
  "url": "https://www.qbitai.com/2025/02/251368.html",
  "date": "2025-02-07 10:01:16",
  "author": "西风",
  "siteName": "量子位",
  "content": "<!--摘要样式-->\n<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <blockquote data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <p class=\"pgc-h-arrow-right\" data-track=\"46\">西风 发自 凹非寺</p>\n   <p class=\"pgc-h-arrow-right\" data-track=\"47\">量子位 | 公众号 QbitAI</p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p data-track=\"2\">“欧洲OpenAI”<strong>Mistral AI</strong>有新动作了！</p>\n  <p data-track=\"3\"><strong>Le Chat</strong>（法语“猫”）<strong>全新升级</strong>，官方自称它是“您生活和工作的终极AI助手”。</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ace6b492-05fc-429f-c521-0d4e70179900/public\" alt=\"免费功能卷翻付费版ChatGPT，欧洲AI新贵叫板OpenAI\" data-ic=\"false\" data-width=\"1080\" data-height=\"794\" data-ic-uri=\"\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"4\">从今天开始，Le Chat上线移动端，<strong>iOS和Android都支持</strong>，不久也将对企业私有基础设施开放。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"5\">功能方面，Le Chat升级主打极速响应，Mistral AI开发者关系主管原话是这样婶儿的：</p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p data-track=\"6\">Le Chat的推理、反思和响应速度超过任何其它聊天助手，可达每秒~1000words。</p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p data-track=\"7\">这个功能被命名为“<strong>闪电回答</strong>”（Flash Answers）。</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/bfada5d8-a7a4-42dc-00fc-fd49bd016700/public\" alt=\"免费功能卷翻付费版ChatGPT，欧洲AI新贵叫板OpenAI\" data-ic=\"false\" data-width=\"1080\" data-height=\"381\" data-ic-uri=\"\">\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/5e8770d7-b89e-4fd1-d1e8-caa36562f800/public\" alt=\"免费功能卷翻付费版ChatGPT，欧洲AI新贵叫板OpenAI\" data-ic=\"false\" data-width=\"1026\" data-height=\"562\" data-ic-uri=\"\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"8\">有多快？</p>\n  <p data-track=\"9\">来看Le Chat与Claude、ChatGPT的对比，同样是用Python编写贪吃蛇游戏，Le Chat刚开始就结束，速度达1100tok/s，Claude速度120tok/s，ChatGPT为85tok/s。</p>\n  <div class=\"syl-plugin-video\" data-data=\"{&quot;vid&quot;:&quot;v02798g10002cuisk2nog65iujqf8u10&quot;,&quot;vu&quot;:&quot;v02798g10002cuisk2nog65iujqf8u10&quot;,&quot;vname&quot;:&quot;X2Twitter.com_WfubFdRdcI8rm4DO_720p.mp4&quot;,&quot;vposter&quot;:&quot;https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-p-e5b010/ee4c95817ed0642d99c6b9ceb28653a2~tplv-tt-origin.image?_iz=30575&amp;lk3s=993df49e&amp;x-expires=1739523236&amp;x-signature=Cj%2F6xr77d9mIfqsk%2FldnbtJ4Egc%3D&quot;,&quot;thumb_url&quot;:&quot;tos-cn-p-e5b010/ee4c95817ed0642d99c6b9ceb28653a2&quot;,&quot;duration&quot;:52.928}\">\n   <img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-251410\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/a985ac73-7ebd-488b-0cae-c054fe695b00/public\" alt=\"免费功能卷翻付费版ChatGPT，欧洲AI新贵叫板OpenAI\" width=\"300\" height=\"168\" srcset=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8d9b7ed4-6111-4f24-bf61-59fdbc00dc00/public 300w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/896519a0-8387-4935-0389-57395f580000/public 768w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4dd905ac-f08e-4e46-f8fc-430327873000/public 1024w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/fcc4a34d-7e42-4b8a-d61b-acac7ad11e00/public 1200w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/fa71e698-18b3-491f-2c64-9b08dc204d00/public 1318w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 85vw, 300px\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"11\">视频链接：https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/K_krY5nLog3dFaQFWIhXdw?token=762419720&amp;lang=zh_CN</p>\n  <p data-track=\"11\">除了速度快，Le Chat还引入了<strong>代码解释器</strong>功能，加上原有的图像生成、高级文档与图像分析、网页搜索、Canvas等，Mistral AI势要和ChatGPT、Claude等卷到底。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"12\">要知道，Canvas等功能在ChatGPT那儿是要付费的，而Le Chat直接免费就能玩，包括“闪电回答”也是免费的。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"13\">而付费版在免费版的功能基础上，外加不限量访问最高性能模型和网页浏览、可选择不与Mistral AI共享数据等权限。Mistral AI表示还将推出私有预览的企业版（Enterprise）。</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/65de1f80-7000-4c2c-14bb-914bad20f900/public\" alt=\"免费功能卷翻付费版ChatGPT，欧洲AI新贵叫板OpenAI\" data-ic=\"false\" data-width=\"1080\" data-height=\"605\" data-ic-uri=\"\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"14\">这波操作把网友看懵:</p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p data-track=\"15\">不明白你们为什么要和ChatGPT/Claude竞争，很烧钱，不是吗？</p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f7071b9c-575f-411a-e486-585dd1fbe200/public\" alt=\"免费功能卷翻付费版ChatGPT，欧洲AI新贵叫板OpenAI\" data-ic=\"false\" data-width=\"1080\" data-height=\"197\" data-ic-uri=\"\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"16\">网友评论区底下直呼：</p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p data-track=\"17\">还需要MacOS app～</p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c788ea55-b555-4b30-f5d1-6296506fbd00/public\" alt=\"免费功能卷翻付费版ChatGPT，欧洲AI新贵叫板OpenAI\" data-ic=\"false\" data-width=\"1080\" data-height=\"228\" data-ic-uri=\"\">\n  </div>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p data-track=\"18\">AI公司一个周内互相超越。</p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/80d3edc7-c3fb-44bf-5268-fb717b1ad400/public\" alt=\"免费功能卷翻付费版ChatGPT，欧洲AI新贵叫板OpenAI\" data-ic=\"false\" data-width=\"1080\" data-height=\"263\" data-ic-uri=\"\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"20\">再具体来看看Le Chat这波新增的代码解释器功能，Le Chat现已具备高级编码功能。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"21\">它使用户能够执行沙箱代码、进行科学分析、创建可视化以及运行模拟。</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f0c3df19-8dcc-4990-6f68-b25740526d00/public\" alt=\"免费功能卷翻付费版ChatGPT，欧洲AI新贵叫板OpenAI\" data-ic=\"false\" data-width=\"1080\" data-height=\"480\" data-ic-uri=\"\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"22\"><strong>比如prompt：</strong>你能解释一下泰勒级数近似的原理吗？给一些正弦函数的例子。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"23\">Le Chat解释时会附带插图说明（Illustration）：</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img src=\"https://www.qbitai.com/wp-content/uploads/replace/7ebd209603518c9977d0b9f297e8a65c.gif\" alt=\"免费功能卷翻付费版ChatGPT，欧洲AI新贵叫板OpenAI\" data-ic=\"false\" data-width=\"558\" data-height=\"346\" data-ic-uri=\"\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"24\">支持验证代码：</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img src=\"https://www.qbitai.com/wp-content/uploads/replace/401845dbbc1a47d92917ed6149f913e2.gif\" alt=\"免费功能卷翻付费版ChatGPT，欧洲AI新贵叫板OpenAI\" data-ic=\"false\" data-width=\"558\" data-height=\"346\" data-ic-uri=\"\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"25\">用代码解释器分析CSV数据也不成问题：</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e7cacafe-9fe2-4137-aaf5-839f52835c00/public\" alt=\"免费功能卷翻付费版ChatGPT，欧洲AI新贵叫板OpenAI\" data-ic=\"false\" data-width=\"504\" data-height=\"302\" data-ic-uri=\"\">\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img src=\"https://www.qbitai.com/wp-content/uploads/replace/47784b34a7e959ca59aaa88073769bd9.gif\" alt=\"免费功能卷翻付费版ChatGPT，欧洲AI新贵叫板OpenAI\" data-ic=\"false\" data-width=\"802\" data-height=\"476\" data-ic-uri=\"\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"26\">Le Chat图像生成功能由Flux Ultra驱动，支持画文字：</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/36a90710-086e-4ea8-6ab2-2ace836acd00/public\" alt=\"免费功能卷翻付费版ChatGPT，欧洲AI新贵叫板OpenAI\" data-ic=\"false\" data-width=\"802\" data-height=\"476\" data-ic-uri=\"\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"27\">也有热门网页搜索功能，附带信息源：</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img src=\"https://www.qbitai.com/wp-content/uploads/replace/3423286fbfafdf37a63555f6625e47ad.gif\" alt=\"免费功能卷翻付费版ChatGPT，欧洲AI新贵叫板OpenAI\" data-ic=\"false\" data-width=\"802\" data-height=\"476\" data-ic-uri=\"\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"28\">文档理解功能，对论文的理解可以精准到某张图，比如可以让它解释Figure 2的abcd都表示啥：</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img src=\"https://www.qbitai.com/wp-content/uploads/replace/425a646a25a676800fc7418f601b1029.gif\" alt=\"免费功能卷翻付费版ChatGPT，欧洲AI新贵叫板OpenAI\" data-ic=\"false\" data-width=\"802\" data-height=\"476\" data-ic-uri=\"\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"29\">除此之外，官方还表示即将对所有用户开放“<strong>记忆</strong>”（Memories）功能，可选择性开启。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"30\">它可以了解记住用户偏好，重新发现很久以前的对话，由此能提供个性化学习，跟踪用户实现目标的进度。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"31\">比如它能记起你之前提到新年目标是在接下来的6个月内将体脂率从22%降至12%，然后帮你制定月度计划：</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/292db0e0-4d4b-45c6-321c-25ef6392f000/public\" alt=\"免费功能卷翻付费版ChatGPT，欧洲AI新贵叫板OpenAI\" data-ic=\"false\" data-width=\"782\" data-height=\"476\" data-ic-uri=\"\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"32\">总之，ChatGPT有的，都得有。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"33\">这就不得不提ChatGPT的会员专属高级界面Canvas功能，Le Chat免费，能够帮助用户从0-1进行创作。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"34\">比如，计划未来四周内在巴黎向另一半求婚，已经买了戒指，但还没有计划其它的细节，请求创建一个详细的视觉时间线以保持事情的进展有序。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"35\">Le Chat的规划是酱婶儿的，有单独界面展示生成的文稿，也有代码以及可视化。</p>\n  <div class=\"syl-plugin-video\" data-data=\"{&quot;vid&quot;:&quot;v02798g10002cuisk6nog65iuh8cig10&quot;,&quot;vu&quot;:&quot;v02798g10002cuisk6nog65iuh8cig10&quot;,&quot;vname&quot;:&quot;X2Twitter.com_yWBxPYXLC1bfG1FH_720p.mp4&quot;,&quot;vposter&quot;:&quot;https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-p-e5b010/4f9cd8f0d1c6241769609cf13b8a7c18~tplv-tt-origin.image?_iz=30575&amp;lk3s=993df49e&amp;x-expires=1739523254&amp;x-signature=4hhSY5FAYhbCsyFvlC9izK65y04%3D&quot;,&quot;thumb_url&quot;:&quot;tos-cn-p-e5b010/4f9cd8f0d1c6241769609cf13b8a7c18&quot;,&quot;duration&quot;:35.166667}\">\n   <img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-251411\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/9c6bca39-13fd-4de9-c0fb-3b551cc18d00/public\" alt=\"免费功能卷翻付费版ChatGPT，欧洲AI新贵叫板OpenAI\" width=\"300\" height=\"168\" srcset=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8897779e-ff4d-4f8d-8de6-f79c27feb800/public 300w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/7e39ab2c-c23e-4314-311e-2fe223e54700/public 768w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/1bb06598-eded-490e-c81b-76aa84a9ec00/public 1024w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/17f0584a-ae80-4fd7-b14a-78cf1dd46f00/public 1200w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/09487f43-d6c0-4e34-e17c-9bfa140c0a00/public 1328w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 85vw, 300px\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"11\">视频链接：https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/K_krY5nLog3dFaQFWIhXdw?token=762419720&amp;lang=zh_CN</p>\n  <p data-track=\"37\">Le Chat还有一个功能是可以创建并在对话中@智能体，智能执行任务：</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/297dd378-7401-426e-3214-a23c9329cf00/public\" alt=\"免费功能卷翻付费版ChatGPT，欧洲AI新贵叫板OpenAI\" data-ic=\"false\" data-width=\"1080\" data-height=\"433\" data-ic-uri=\"\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"38\">比如使用Le Chat智能体追踪个人财务，自动化安排日程：</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img src=\"https://www.qbitai.com/wp-content/uploads/replace/43715e32d85e4906d9df3f42e310de29.gif\" alt=\"免费功能卷翻付费版ChatGPT，欧洲AI新贵叫板OpenAI\" data-ic=\"false\" data-width=\"782\" data-height=\"476\" data-ic-uri=\"\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"39\">都能get可视化图表的那种：</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <img src=\"https://www.qbitai.com/wp-content/uploads/replace/983b04aa4e269e6dc91735173a200bcb.gif\" alt=\"免费功能卷翻付费版ChatGPT，欧洲AI新贵叫板OpenAI\" data-ic=\"false\" data-width=\"782\" data-height=\"476\" data-ic-uri=\"\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"40\">Le Chat全新升级后，网友们也已经开始玩起来了。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"41\">有网友尝试一番过后反馈确实很快：</p>\n  <div class=\"syl-plugin-video\" data-data=\"{&quot;vid&quot;:&quot;v02798g10002cuisk9fog65pegoh2m00&quot;,&quot;vu&quot;:&quot;v02798g10002cuisk9fog65pegoh2m00&quot;,&quot;vname&quot;:&quot;X2Twitter.com_9kQCLyJ-tDU85rC6_720p.mp4&quot;,&quot;vposter&quot;:&quot;https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-p-e5b010/b70c8813f35739b3b2e41546d5365a07~tplv-tt-origin.image?_iz=30575&amp;lk3s=993df49e&amp;x-expires=1739523257&amp;x-signature=hyg9AMJuuttN657G6%2B9frU7eaeA%3D&quot;,&quot;thumb_url&quot;:&quot;tos-cn-p-e5b010/b70c8813f35739b3b2e41546d5365a07&quot;,&quot;duration&quot;:46.65}\">\n   &nbsp;<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-251412\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/469fb7dc-0714-4bc1-a81d-7b6624c57000/public\" alt=\"免费功能卷翻付费版ChatGPT，欧洲AI新贵叫板OpenAI\" width=\"300\" height=\"224\" srcset=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4529db84-38f6-4458-b816-6b919d0fe800/public 300w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/bb039d4b-4c1a-4354-c1b9-358c6233ad00/public 768w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/133f60a5-d94a-4650-e857-bea7c0617f00/public 1024w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/34d64962-7bbc-4189-6f55-3b1f36e6dd00/public 1200w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/fac85af5-07c3-4e24-fdfe-c8f7ed0ba900/public 1334w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 85vw, 300px\">\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"43\">视频链接：https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/K_krY5nLog3dFaQFWIhXdw?token=762419720&amp;lang=zh_CN</p>\n  <p data-track=\"43\">感兴趣的童鞋可以亲自试试～</p>\n  <p data-track=\"44\">chat.mistral.ai/chat</p>\n  <p data-track=\"45\">参考链接：<br>\n    [1]https://x.com/sophiamyang/status/1887517050697842899<br>\n    [2]https://x.com/onetwoval/status/1887547069956845634<br>\n    [3]https://x.com/MistralAI/status/1887517520040448510</p><!--版权声明-->\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "Mistral AI 旗下 Le Chat 全新升级，推出免费移动端应用并增加多种功能，旨在通过免费策略挑战 ChatGPT 和 Claude。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Mistral AI 旗下 Le Chat 全新升级，推出免费移动端应用并增加多种功能，旨在通过免费策略挑战 ChatGPT 和 Claude。",
  "summary": "文章报道了 Mistral AI 对其 AI 聊天助手 Le Chat 的重大升级。Le Chat 现在支持 iOS 和 Android 移动端，并增加了包括代码解释器在内的新功能，旨在与 ChatGPT 和 Claude 等领先的 AI 助手竞争，目标用户群体包括开发者、科研人员等。Le Chat 强调其“闪电回答”功能，声称具有卓越的推理和响应速度。此外，Le Chat 还提供图像生成、高级文档分析、网页搜索和 Canvas 等功能，其中许多功能在 ChatGPT 中需要付费才能使用。Mistral AI 还计划推出企业版，并即将推出“记忆”功能，记忆用户偏好，提供个性化学习和目标跟踪。文章通过对比测试和用户反馈，展示了 Le Chat 的功能和性能，以及 Mistral AI 在 AI 助手市场的雄心。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "Le Chat 采取差异化竞争策略，通过免费提供多种功能，挑战 ChatGPT 和 Claude 的付费模式。",
